091Sm 8:6 But when they said, "Give us a king to lead us," this displeased Samuel; so he prayed to the LORD.
091Sm 8:7 And the LORD told him£º "Listen to all that the people are saying to you; it is not you they have rejected, but they have rejected me as their king.
091Sm 8:8 As they have done from the day I brought them up out of Egypt until this day, forsaking me and serving other gods, so they are doing to you.
