091Sm 13:10 Just as he finished making the offering, Samuel arrived, and Saul went out to greet him.
091Sm 13:11 "What have you done?" asked Samuel. Saul replied, "When I saw that the men were scattering, and that you did not come at the set time, and that the Philistines were assembling at Micmash,
