091Sm 21:13 So he pretended to be insane in their presence; and while he was in their hands he acted like a madman, making marks on the doors of the gate and letting saliva run down his beard.
091Sm 21:14 Achish said to his servants, "Look at the man! He is insane! Why bring him to me?
