091Sm 22:22 Then David said to Abiathar£º "That day, when Doeg the Edomite was there, I knew he would be sure to tell Saul. I am responsible for the death of your father's whole family.
091Sm 22:23 Stay with me; don't be afraid; the man who is seeking your life is seeking mine also. You will be safe with me."
091Sm 23:1 When David was told, "Look, the Philistines are fighting against Keilah and are looting the threshing floors,"
