091Sm 24:6 He said to his men, "The LORD forbid that I should do such a thing to my master, the LORD'S anointed, or lift my hand against him; for he is the anointed of the LORD."
091Sm 24:7 With these words David rebuked his men and did not allow them to attack Saul. And Saul left the cave and went his way.
