091Sm 24:22 So David gave his oath to Saul. Then Saul returned home, but David and his men went up to the stronghold.
091Sm 25:1 Now Samuel died, and all Israel assembled and mourned for him; and they buried him at his home in Ramah. Then David moved down into the Desert of Maon.
