091Sm 25:5 So he sent ten young men and said to them, "Go up to Nabal at Carmel and greet him in my name.
091Sm 25:6 Say to him£º 'Long life to you! Good health to you and your household! And good health to all that is yours!
091Sm 25:7 "'Now I hear that it is sheep-shearing time. When your shepherds were with us, we did not mistreat them, and the whole time they were at Carmel nothing of theirs was missing.
